<div
  style="font-family: Arial, sans-serif; max-width: 600px; margin: auto; padding: 20px; background-color: #f9f9f9; border: 1px solid #ddd; border-radius: 8px;"
>
  <div style="text-align: center;">
    <img
      src="https://res.cloudinary.com/dh2lr5aya/image/upload/w_1000,ar_1:1,c_fill,g_auto,e_art:hokusai/v1728321079/Gas-Station-Pro-logo_gmzb8j.webp"
      alt="Gas Station Pro Logo"
      style="width: 150px; margin-bottom: 20px;"
    />
  </div>
  <div style="background-color: #ffffff; padding: 20px; border-radius: 8px;">
    <h2 style="color: #333;">Hello {{ownerName}},</h2>

    <p style="color: #555;">
      We would like to inform you that the sales report for your store
      <strong>{{storeName}}</strong>
      has been updated.
    </p>

    <p style="color: #555;">
      The report was edited by
      <strong>{{name}}</strong>
      on
      <strong>{{updatedDate}}</strong>.
    </p>

    <p style="color: #555;">
      You can view the updated sales report by logging into your account using
      the link below:
    </p>

    <div style="text-align: center; margin: 20px 0;">
      <a
        href="{{link}}"
        clicktracking="off"
        style="background-color: #007bff; color: #ffffff; text-decoration: none; padding: 15px 25px; border-radius: 5px; font-weight: bold; display: inline-block;"
      >View Updated Sales Report</a>
    </div>

    <p style="color: #555;">Alternatively, you can click on the link below to
      access the report directly:</p>
    <p>
      <a href="{{link}}" clicktracking="off" style="color: #007bff;">
        {{link}}
      </a>
    </p>

    <hr style="margin: 30px 0;" />

    <p style="font-size: 0.9rem; color: #777;">
      If you have any questions or concerns about this update, please contact
      our support team.
    </p>

    <p style="color: #333;">
      Regards,<br />
      <strong>The Gas Station Pro Team</strong>
    </p>
  </div>
</div>